---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Where to Go When">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-playfair text-5xl mb-8 text-center">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
      <p class="lead text-xl mb-6">
        We believe that timing is everything when it comes to creating unforgettable travel experiences.
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-6">
        Our mission is simple: to inspire and guide travelers in making informed decisions about their next adventure. 
        We understand that choosing where to go can be overwhelming, which is why we've created a platform that 
        simplifies the decision-making process by focusing on the most crucial factor - timing.
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-6">
        Whether you're chasing the perfect weather, trying to catch a once-in-a-lifetime festival, or looking to 
        avoid tourist crowds, our carefully curated recommendations ensure you're in the right place at the right time.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="font-playfair text-3xl mt-12 mb-6">Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>
        Every destination, every recommendation, and every piece of advice we share is thoroughly researched and 
        often personally experienced by our team of passionate travelers. We're dedicated to providing up-to-date, 
        practical information that helps you make the most of your travels.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>